                <span>Science-driven approach</span>
              </div>
              <div class="highlight">
                <span class="highlight-icon">ü§ù</span>
                <span>Community partnerships</span>
              </div>
              <div class="highlight">
                <span class="highlight-icon">üåç</span>
                <span>Global reach, local action</span>
              </div>
