        <div class="section-header">
          <span class="section-label">What We Do</span>
          <h2>Our Programs</h2>
          <p>From local beach cleanups to international policy work, we're tackling ocean conservation from every angle.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="programs-grid">
          <div class="program-card">
            <div class="program-icon">üê¢</div>
