            <p>Protecting endangered marine species through habitat restoration, rescue operations, and breeding programs.</p>
            <a href="#" class="program-link">Learn more ‚Üí</a>
          </div>
          <div class="program-card">
            <div class="program-icon">üèñÔ∏è</div>
            <h3>Clean Coasts</h3>
            <p>Organizing beach cleanups and working with communities to reduce plastic waste entering our oceans.</p>
            <a href="#" class="program-link">Learn more ‚Üí</a>
          </div>
          <div class="program-card">
            <div class="program-icon">üìö</div>
            <h3>Ocean Education</h3>
            <p>Teaching the next generation about marine ecosystems through school programs and interactive workshops.</p>
            <a href="#" class="program-link">Learn more ‚Üí</a>
          </div>
          <div class="program-card">
            <div class="program-icon">üèõÔ∏è</div>
            <h3>Policy Advocacy</h3>
            <p>Working with governments to establish marine protected areas and strengthen environmental regulations.</p>
            <a href="#" class="program-link">Learn more ‚Üí</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Impact Stories -->
    <section class="stories" id="impact">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header">
          <span class="section-label">Making a Difference</span>
          <h2>Impact Stories</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="stories-grid">
          <div class="story-card story-card--featured">
            <div class="story-image story-image--coral"></div>
            <div class="story-content">
              <span class="story-tag">Success Story</span>
              <h3>Coral Reef Restoration in the Philippines</h3>
              <p>How our team helped restore 15 hectares of damaged coral reef, bringing back biodiversity to a once-devastated ecosystem.</p>
              <a href="#" class="story-link">Read the full story ‚Üí</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="story-card">
            <div class="story-image story-image--turtle"></div>
            <div class="story-content">
              <h3>Sea Turtle Rescue Program</h3>
              <p>Our rehabilitation center has released over 500 sea turtles back into the wild.</p>
              <a href="#" class="story-link">Read more ‚Üí</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="story-card">
            <div class="story-image story-image--cleanup"></div>
            <div class="story-content">
              <h3>1 Million Pounds Removed</h3>
              <p>Our Clean Coasts program hit a major milestone in ocean plastic removal.</p>
              <a href="#" class="story-link">Read more ‚Üí</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Get Involved -->
